y goal\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"a former world champion\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so grateful and so happy to come out with the win but more than anything, I just wanted to show the world what breaking is.\\\"\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"what breaking\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition saw 16 dancers, known as B-Boys, going head-to-head in a series of battles, starting with a pool stage before moving to a knock-out round.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"16 dancers\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"B-Boys\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"battles\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool stage\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"a knock-out round\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phil Wizard had the crowd against him in the final against local hero Dany Dann, a 36-year-old with blue hair whose real name is Danis Civil.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Phil Wizard\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"local hero Dany Dann\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"blue hair\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"whose real name\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"Danis Civil\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Canadian soon had them eating out of his hand thanks to his incredible routine, for which the judges awarded him a 3-0 victory.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9735911281744847, \"rank\": 0.026263536005140253, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his hand\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"his incredible routine\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3-0 victory\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was stressed out of my mind,\\\" said Phil Wizard.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"Phil Wizard\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a whirlwind of emotion.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whirlwind\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cried my eyes out because I was so scared to do this.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my eyes\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is been a lot of pressure, a lot of expectations - I am glad I was able to deliver.\\\"\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Danny Dann, a former European champion, said he felt like he had \\\"represented breaking\\\" to the world.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1794, \"title\":